UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 383
1 (3) It shall be unlawful for any person who is listed on the nurse aide abuse registry
2 with a substantiated finding of abuse, neglect, or misappropriation of property to
3 provide licensed lactation consultation.
4 (4) Sections 1 to 5 of this Act shall not apply to a licensed health care provider
5 rendering services that are within his or her scope of practice.
